title: Game Theory and Money Podcast: Week 11 Predictions
itunes:title: Game Theory and Money Podcast: Week 11 Predictions
description:
Who comes out on top most between the Chiefs and Rams after you run 10-thousand computer simulations? And will there really be a million points scored? What about Vikings-Bears? Eagles-Saints? Well don't waste your time coming up with all that code because Cynthia Frelund already did it and she has the results for every week 11 game in the NFL. Find the game you want by checking out the time codes listed below!


Eagles-Saints (5:20). Packers-Seahawks (11:30). Texans-Redskins (18:50). Cowboys-Falcons (22:50). Buccaneers-Giants (27:00). Steelers-Jaguars (28:25). Broncos-Chargers (31:25). Raiders-Cardinals (38:00). Chiefs-Rams (41:35). Panthers-Lions (49:30). Vikings-Bears (52:30). Titans-Colts (59:30). TOP 3 CONFIDENCE PICKS (1:03:45). NFC PLAYOFF PROJECTIONS (1:04:20). AFC PLAYOFF PROJECTIONS (1:06:40)
